{"word":"G1468 - ἐγκρατής - enkratḗs - eng-krat-ace' - Temperate","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐγκρατής</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">enkratḗs</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">eng-krat-ace'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Temperate</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"இச்சையடக்கமுள்ள - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"mastering, controlling, curbing, restraining"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1722 - ἐν - en - en/1722\">G1722</a> and <a href=\"#/G2904 - κράτος - krátos - krat'-os/2904\">G2904</a>; <i>strong in</i> a thing (<i>masterful</i>), that is, (figuratively and reflexively) <i>self controlled</i> (in appetite, etc.): - temperate.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1466/1466\">G1466</a>, <a href=\"#/G1467/1467\">G1467</a>, <a href=\"#/G1468/1468\">G1468</a>, <a href=\"#/G192/192\">G192</a>, <a href=\"#/G193/193\">G193</a>"}]}